{
  "name": "Poltergeist",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/death.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may make a ghost strike that attaches a vengeful poltergeist to the target, disrupting their actions. Whenever the target makes a d20 roll within 1 round per caster level, you can choose for them take a -3 penalty to the roll, ending this effect. This penalty is increased by 1 for every 6 caster levels you have.</p>\n<p>If you spend a spell point when you use this ghost strike, you can impose the penalty on up to one d20 roll the target makes each round for the effect&#8217;s duration, and imposing the penalty does not end the effect. A creature can only be affected by one poltergeist at a time.</p>\n",
